	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accepi literas tuas amicissimas et gracias primum ago et habeo propter significationem novarum, quae tibi constare potuerunt.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mirum vero artificium Satanae <placeName ref="l425" cert="high">Romae</placeName> declaratum, ci se organum <persName type="auto_name">Tammerus</persName> praebuit, nefarius syncerae religionis praevaricator relaturus cum <persName type="auto_name">Iuda</persName>, nisi mature resipisceret, dignum impietatis praemium.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nihil non tentat ea pestilentiae sedes confundenda potenti manu excelsi.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Instat urgetque pontifex apud Ferdinandumet eius generum <persName cert="high" type="citizen_name">Albertum</persName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l619" cert="high">Bavariae</placeName> ducem, ne pientissimis suorum postulatis acquiescant; nam et nobilitas <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l619" cert="high">Bavarica</placeName> idem a suo duce contendit, quod <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l850" cert="high">Austriaca</placeName> a rege <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20743" cert="high">Ferdinando</persName>; sed pro utroque per literas et legatos respondet bestia, quod ad se, non ad principes spectet religionis administratio.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l303" cert="high">Magdenburgenses</placeName> cum suo archiepiscopo et electoribus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l749" cert="high">Saxone</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1048" cert="high">Brandenburgense</placeName> de controversia transegerunt, quam habuerunt gravem et ad bellum spectantem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sunt, qui augurentur ducem <persName type="citizen_name">Volphgangum</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2477">Palatinum</placeName> bello petiturum fines <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augustani</placeName> cardinalis, eo quid <placeName ref="l425" cert="high">Romae</placeName> nescio quid machinatus sit contra <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2477">Palatinos</placeName> comites.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Norici implorant auxilia; sed nescitur contra quem; adeo varie aestuant res <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germaniae</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pro libris ad te non scripsissem, si scivissem donaturum; accipio tamen donum animo gratissimo idque ita, ut de gratitudinis significatione sim cogitaturus, sicuti par est.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale in Christo Iesu, quia pluribus non possum propter capitis vertiginem; antehac inconsuetam mihi pati hodie cępi.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salvos iube meis verbis amanter tuos omnes.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileae</placeName> 26. februarii anno 1556.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Qui has perfert, iuvenis vere pius est bonorum omnium testimonio; quem tibi commendo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3099" cert="high">Sulcerus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Viro clarissimo d. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heinricho Bullingero</persName>, ecclesiae <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurinae</placeName> pastori vigilantissimo, domino et symmistae colendissimo suo.</s>
				</p>
